{"tid":592225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[用完即棄] 遊戲無以為繼 Fruit Ninja 開發商大裁員","createTime":"2018-03-14T04:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T08:09:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e876e64665bf08d861679a63f69466e8c2680ff","tid":592225,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"在競爭激烈的手機遊戲行業，要站穩陣腳並不容易，就算能夠成功開發出一款風靡全球的遊戲，亦無法確保前途從此就一片光明。在 2010 年 4 月推出的手機遊戲《Fruit Ninja》，可算是首批在智能手機取得佳績的遊戲，隨著智能手機剛興起，玩法簡單的《Fruit Ninja》大受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/0314-2a.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F0314-2a.jpg&d=YFFXd4KYqv50WCakF7OTpjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=8243ec74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/0314-2a.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n《Fruit Ninja》創下了近 10 億下載的佳績，還未計算在非官方渠道的下載量。可惜開發者遊戲的 Halfbrick 工作室在過去 7、8 年都無法再開發出媲美《Fruit Ninja》的手機遊戲，當中只有《Jetpack Joyride》較受歡迎，其他遊戲的表現乏善足陳。最近公司宣佈大幅裁員，是繼 2015 年<span style=\"color: red;\">炒掉大量遊戲設計員工後的第二波</span>，今次裁員 30 人約為公司近半員工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/14/fruit-ninja-cut-jobs/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2Ffruit-ninja-cut-jobs%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=YFFXd4KYqv50WCakF7OTpjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=85209aaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/14/fruit-ninja-cut-jobs/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"15aa4d3576074a65605e09f72b740fc5488ab1b4","tid":592225,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/0314-2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F0314-2a.jpg&h=75084f8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cb77542fb2c6966627e9ff149212da0d19b33b4","tid":592225,"uid":169992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"